Florence Welch is the charismatic flameheaded frontwoman of Florence and The Machine one of the most innovative contemporary bands around PERIOD The bands debut and only album to date Lungs was released in July  but didnt reach commercial success in the United States until late last year PERIOD  This is a massive shame as Lungs is completely life changing PERIOD

Dog Days are Over is the perfect song to chuck on at the start of a road trip or the end of finals week PERIOD It is impossible to listen to this song without pulling an awkward dance move while walking around campus PERIOD Drumming Song will drill a hole in the listeners head and plant its lyrics for days PERIOD Ceaseless chanting of Theres a drumming noise inside my head  that starts when youre around is completely inescapable PERIOD Cosmic Love is a magical dichotomous blend of both the end of a relationship and the start of one PERIOD On one hand there is A falling star fell from your heart and landed in my eyes and on the other The stars the moon they have all been blown out  you left me in the dark. however the album ends with an exploding firework of a song Youve Got the Love. welch sings about throwing her hands in the air eating her mate for sustenance and simply having the love to see her through PERIOD A choral anthem forms the backdrop for this uplifting ballad that wraps Lungs in a perfect package of an album PERIOD
